## How to Add

Open `.gitignore` in IntelliJ and paste those lines at the **bottom** of the file.

---

## Your File is Already Covering
```
✅ target/          ← compiled code not pushed
✅ .idea/           ← IntelliJ config not pushed
✅ *.iml            ← IntelliJ files not pushed
✅ .mvn/            ← Maven wrapper not pushed
